{"tid":2031722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本京成電鐵FB舉「香港加油」","createTime":"2020-05-23T14:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T15:13:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7f476a36cb97c864c5a3e85bb734d15dc85e1848","tid":2031722,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/w1bfiYcsBeVZmNQxvK8OkQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNC42NjY2NjY2NjY2NjY3/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/q6U7XrntMDneoG31LQUOeA--~B/aD02Mzc7dz05NjA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200523a191352.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fw1bfiYcsBeVZmNQxvK8OkQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNC42NjY2NjY2NjY2NjY3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fq6U7XrntMDneoG31LQUOeA--~B%2FaD02Mzc7dz05NjA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200523a191352.jpg&h=0e28db99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本東京私鐵「京成電鐵」今天在facebook「京成電鐵 Keisei Skyliner」發表一張照片，員工手持「香港加油」 標語，為香港加油。帖文超過2000人轉載，還有過千個香港網民湧去留言，紛紛表示「多謝日本朋友」、「期待再次到日本旅行」等。<br />\n<br />\n「京成電鐵」在facebook上載圖片鼓勵香港抗疫，「香港的朋友們，我們一直都支持著你們。持續勤洗手勤漱口吧！香港加油！！一起加油！！打起精神！期待再次見面！由衷期待疫情結束後與大家交流。日本加油，香港加油！」<br />\n<br />\n雖然整篇帖文隻字無提香港近期的《國安法》爭議、反修例示威等字眼，但仍然有不少香港網民將「香港加油」聯想成政治含義，留言寫道，「感謝支持香港民主既日本朋友」、「光復香港！時代革命！」、「Thank you for supporting freedom and democracy」（多謝支持自由和民主）、「Fight for Freedom」（爭取自由）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/日本京成電鐵fb舉-香港加油-過千網民留言感謝-134200629.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%AC%E6%88%90%E9%9B%BB%E9%90%B5fb%E8%88%89-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%B9-%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%83%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D-134200629.html&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=29126f91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/日本京成電鐵fb舉-香港加油-過千網民留言感謝-134200629.html</a>"},{"pid":"cf2b7ec742cae8104b00b0e0e477c5eae7656809","tid":2031722,"uid":348453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:56:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a817fcb57a1b4338617370210989b4b77f1b55d8","tid":2031722,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:59:51.000Z","msg":"點解我淨係見到台灣加油張相"},{"pid":"1b3069f94971c8cc961101c8bf43d93a35ef3fd9","tid":2031722,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f476a36cb97c864c5a3e85bb734d15dc85e1848","tid":2031722,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/w1bfiYcsBeVZmNQxvK8OkQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNC42NjY2NjY2NjY2NjY3/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/q6U7XrntMDneoG31LQUOeA--~B/aD02Mzc7dz05NjA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200523a191352.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fw1bfiYcsBeVZmNQxvK8OkQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNC42NjY2NjY2NjY2NjY3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fq6U7XrntMDneoG31LQUOeA--~B%2FaD02Mzc7dz05NjA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200523a191352.jpg&h=0e28db99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本東京私鐵「京成電鐵」今天在facebook「京成電鐵 Keisei Skyliner」發表一張照片，員工手持「香港加油」 標語，為香港加油。帖文超過2000人轉載，還有過千個香港網民湧去留言，紛紛表示「多謝日本朋友」、「期待再次到日本旅行」等。<br />\n<br />\n「京成電鐵」在facebook上載圖片鼓勵香港抗疫，「香港的朋友們，我們一直都支持著你們。持續勤洗手勤漱口吧！香港加油！！一起加油！！打起精神！期待再次見面！由衷期待疫情結束後與大家交流。日本加油，香港加油！」<br />\n<br />\n雖然整篇帖文隻字無提香港近期的《國安法》爭議、反修例示威等字眼，但仍然有不少香港網民將「香港加油」聯想成政治含義，留言寫道，「感謝支持香港民主既日本朋友」、「光復香港！時代革命！」、「Thank you for supporting freedom and democracy」（多謝支持自由和民主）、「Fight for Freedom」（爭取自由）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/日本京成電鐵fb舉-香港加油-過千網民留言感謝-134200629.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news